Paper: hep-th/0111191

Date: 2001-11-21

Title: Perturbation theory and renormalisation group equations

Authors: Daniel F. Litim, Jan M. Pawlowski

Comments: 5 pages, 1 figure, revtex, typos corrected, eq. (19) added,

discussion extended, to appear in PRDJournal-ref: Phys.Rev. D65 (2002) 081701

We discuss the perturbative expansion of several one-loop improvedrenormalisation group equations. It is shown that in general the integratedrenormalisation group flows fail to reproduce perturbation theory beyond oneloop.